Dustin Thiry - Millennials

Jan 29, 2016

Different by design: a runner, husband, father, and struggling vegetarian. Dustin Thiry has worked to try to change the culture of Wichita’s biggest economies, sometimes you’ve got to be different. This means digging deep, and re-thinking “the way things are”.

Favorite Thing About Wichita:
“The potential.”
